Let $r(\theta) = \frac{1}{1-\theta}$. What is $r(r(r(r(r(r(30))))))$ (where $r$ is applied $6$ times)? ||| We evaluate $r$ several times to see if there is a pattern. Indeed, $r(\theta) = \frac{1}{1-\theta}$, so \begin{align*}
